OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy rain
OL,6,Fduring the evening will become more
OL,7,Fwidespread from the late evening.
OL,8,FOrkney will see the best of any dry
OL,9,Fspells towards the morning. Windy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FOvernight rain soon clearing
OL,12,Fthrough the morning. Then it will be a
OL,13,Fdry day with some spells of sunshine.
OL,14,FStrong southeasterly winds across
OL,15,FShetland at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
