OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FEarly
OL,6,Fshowers clear Shetland Tuesday morning
OL,7,Fleaving the Isles dry with sunny
OL,8,Fspells until early Thursday. Outbreaks
OL,9,Fof rain spread east over the Isles
OL,10,Ffrom Thursday afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
